{"tid":996641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] Angelababy拍停食穿山甲通乳廣告 被狂轟曲線宣傳","createTime":"2019-01-26T12:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T13:15:20.000Z","uid":123920,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"771292f382ccc1a1fa0b729243ad42bd53cb9f3e","tid":996641,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"話說，Angelababy早前為國際環保組織「動物救援」拍攝廣告，宣揚保護保護瀕臨絕種動物穿山甲，不過點知就反被網民狂轟，指佢「愈幫愈忙」！<br />\nAngelababy拍停食穿山甲通乳廣告<br />\n早前，Angelababy為宣揚保護瀕臨絕種動物穿山甲而拍攝一段短片，片中Angelababy手抱一隻穿山甲，並指：「過去10年有近100萬隻穿山甲慘遭殺害，甲片和肉被非法利用，非法藥材不是通乳的選擇，讓每一隻穿山甲寶寶能在母愛下平安的長大。沒有買賣，就沒有殺害。」<br />\n其後，Angelababy再於自己微博轉發，並寫上：「我承諾不用穿山甲通乳。」，明示自己意向，以支持國際環保組織今次嘅宣揚活動！<br />\n<br />\n網民狂轟曲線宣傳<br />\n本來呢段短片嘅信息好明確同清晰，不過就惹嚟唔少網民狂轟，指Angelababy「幫倒忙」，皆因Angelababy嘅言論並冇澄清到「穿山甲不能通乳」，因而會變相宣傳「穿山甲能通乳」呢個錯誤嘅信息！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/337877/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%A8%9B%E8%81%9E/angelababy-%E6%8B%8D%E5%81%9C%E9%A3%9F%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B2%E9%80%9A%E4%B9%B3%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2F337877%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A8%259B%25E8%2581%259E%2Fangelababy-%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%2594%25B2%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25B9%25B3%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%2F&d=P5qmjWKYo%2FOmEiOTDoYowv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=73cdf472\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientalsunday.hk/337877/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%A8%9B%E8%81%9E/angelababy-%E6%8B%8D%E5%81%9C%E9%A3%9F%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B2%E9%80%9A%E4%B9%B3%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOTRyaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOTRyaf.jpg&h=7210765f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EMKdMvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMKdMvf.jpg&h=3580b5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHW38JB.jpg\" data-thumbna